Package helper

package helper
Contains classes for server-side code not necessarily related to servlets.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    DirectoryHelper
    Contains helper methods for managing the directories of a ServletContext.
    Helper
    Contains general helper methods useful in some parts of the code.
    OWLMaster
    Contains helper methods for interacting with OWL knowledge bases.
    OWLOntologyCreator
    Contains helper methods for the creation of a new ontology.
    SubmitToGitHub
    Contains methods for uploading files to a GitHub repository through GitHub's REST API.
